targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias(created_at,$__interval),
  count(message_id) AS "message_id"
FROM message_logs
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created_at)
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(created_at,$__interval)

SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias(created_at,$__interval),
  count(message_id) AS "message_id"
FROM message_logs
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created_at) AND
  is_dm = '0'
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(created_at,$__interval)

  $__timeGroupAlias(created_at,$__interval),
